  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is conducted in Europe. The aim of this observational study is to describe the
      conditions for the concomitant administration of a slow-acting insulin analogue with oral
      antidiabetics (OADs) in order to improve blood glucose control in type 2 diabetes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
